{
  "texts": [
    "However, unsuccessful cases are not due to lacking capability of the LLM.",
    "In the unsuccessful set, 20.4% of the messages happened because LIVE555 does not support the functionality for \"ANNOUNCE\" and \"RECORD\", despite being included in its RFC.",
    "The remaining cases were attributed to incorrect session IDs in the \"PLAY\", \"TEARDOWN\", \"GET PARAMETER\" and \"SET PARAMETER\" requests.",
    "A session ID is dynamically assigned by the server and included in the server response.",
    "Since the LLM lacks this context information, it is not able to generate a correct session ID."
  ]
}